v><div class="t m148b x15 h2d yc66 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">will be in the earth. If all were to be counterfeit, the Lord </div><div class="t m84d x15 h2d ya0 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">could have said, &quot;Beware of prophets.&quot; </div><div class="t m127 x4a h2d y256 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m102 x29 h2d y169 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">in vision the prophet of the Lord loses his own strength. </div><div class="t m17a x15 h2d y33 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">His breath also is taken away. In this condition, under the </div><div class="t m5e1 x15 h4a yd8d ff6 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;This Gospel of the kingdom shall be preached in all the world </div><div class="t m1cf x26 h4a y882 ff6 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for a witness unto all nations; and then shall the end come.&quot; </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
